1
00:00:22,310 --> 00:00:23,910
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Isn't this...</font>

2
00:00:23,910 --> 00:00:27,340
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}Yes, it's the hole Richeh opened again.</font>

3
00:00:25,590 --> 00:00:30,930
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">{\an1}<font size="18"><font face="Times New Roman"><b>The<font color="#000000"> Dragon's Labyrinth</font></b></font></font></font>

4
00:00:27,340 --> 00:00:28,900
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}How many times is that now?</font>

5
00:00:28,900 --> 00:00:31,140
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}I've lost count.</font>

6
00:00:31,140 --> 00:00:34,890
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Anyway, let's find 
somewhere covered to hide.</font>

7
00:00:34,890 --> 00:00:37,100
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I think it's getting colder in here.</font>

8
00:00:53,290 --> 00:00:55,050
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">T-Tetia.</font>

9
00:00:57,650 --> 00:01:00,080
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You... dropped this.</font>

10
00:01:05,050 --> 00:01:06,550
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Thanks.</font>

11
00:01:08,560 --> 00:01:10,980
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Um... are you okay?</font>

12
00:01:13,960 --> 00:01:15,890
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yeah, I guess not...</font>

13
00:01:16,330 --> 00:01:18,680
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm sorry. This is all my fault.</font>

14
00:01:21,380 --> 00:01:22,440
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And, um...</font>

15
00:01:22,440 --> 00:01:25,390
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Y-You'll be cold without a cloak, 
so wear mine instead!</font>

16
00:01:25,390 --> 00:01:27,070
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'll just snuggle up close!</font>

17
00:01:33,250 --> 00:01:34,560
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Coco?</font>

18
00:01:36,060 --> 00:01:40,150
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I feel really safe when I have it on.</font>

19
00:01:42,110 --> 00:01:46,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">When I'm wearing my cloak, 
nobody can see that I'm shaking with fear.</font>

20
00:01:46,380 --> 00:01:51,140
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Knowing that I still look like a witch 
on the outside helps me be brave.</font>

21
00:01:51,140 --> 00:01:54,410
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">So I want you to wear it right now.</font>

22
00:01:54,410 --> 00:01:57,760
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You'll be a lot more help than I've been.</font>

23
00:02:01,350 --> 00:02:02,480
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What the?!</font>

24
00:02:05,040 --> 00:02:06,610
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What are they doing?</font>

25
00:02:09,640 --> 00:02:11,120
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's warm.</font>

26
00:02:11,510 --> 00:02:12,530
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">A cloud?</font>

27
00:02:13,110 --> 00:02:16,780
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm sorry I looked at you 
like this was your fault!</font>

28
00:02:21,430 --> 00:02:23,980
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's fine. It <i>is</i> my fault, anyway.</font>

29
00:02:23,980 --> 00:02:27,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And it's not like you actually said it...</font>

30
00:02:28,000 --> 00:02:30,270
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">If I acted like it, it's no better.</font>

31
00:02:30,270 --> 00:02:34,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I took my fear out on you.</font>

32
00:02:34,630 --> 00:02:39,150
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I've been doing this longer than you. 
I'm supposed to protect you.</font>

33
00:02:39,670 --> 00:02:40,730
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Tetia...</font>

34
00:02:42,890 --> 00:02:44,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But you <i>are</i> protecting me!</font>

35
00:02:44,420 --> 00:02:46,340
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Look how warm this spell is!</font>

36
00:02:46,340 --> 00:02:48,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I feel super relaxed even 
though we're in danger!</font>

37
00:02:48,290 --> 00:02:50,210
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's amazing! Magic is so powerful!</font>

38
00:02:51,960 --> 00:02:55,400
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's my very own creation.</font>

39
00:02:55,790 --> 00:02:59,810
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">When I was a little kid, 
I dreamed about napping on a cloud.</font>

40
00:02:59,810 --> 00:03:01,910
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">So I've been trying out different things.</font>

41
00:03:01,910 --> 00:03:04,410
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's not finished yet, though.</font>

42
00:03:04,410 --> 00:03:07,580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Once it is, I'd like to 
submit it for approval</font>

43
00:03:07,580 --> 00:03:10,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">as a general-use spell 
for everyone to try.</font>

44
00:03:10,290 --> 00:03:13,020
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It might not be the most 
useful spell out there,</font>

45
00:03:13,020 --> 00:03:15,800
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">but it's my dream, 
and that means a lot to me.</font>

46
00:03:16,120 --> 00:03:18,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">So you should wear your own cloak.</font>

47
00:03:18,500 --> 00:03:21,180
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Let's not take off our novice cloaks 
until we're back home safe</font>

48
00:03:21,180 --> 00:03:24,310
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">and we all become real witches together.</font>

49
00:03:24,670 --> 00:03:25,640
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Okay?</font>

50
00:03:29,210 --> 00:03:30,190
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yeah!</font>

51
00:03:33,850 --> 00:03:34,930
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I heard all that.</font>

52
00:03:35,340 --> 00:03:36,430
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">If you want to lie on top of this,</font>

53
00:03:36,430 --> 00:03:39,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">it needs to be made of 
a substance with more mass.</font>

54
00:03:39,130 --> 00:03:41,190
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Too cold outside.</font>

55
00:03:41,190 --> 00:03:42,520
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Richeh's coming in.</font>

56
00:03:42,520 --> 00:03:44,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">If you want people 
to be able to fly on it,</font>

57
00:03:44,290 --> 00:03:46,910
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">you'll need a cloud-like 
material to substitute.</font>

58
00:03:46,910 --> 00:03:47,780
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Like cotton.</font>

59
00:03:47,780 --> 00:03:50,200
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But then it would just be 
a normal mattress!</font>

60
00:03:50,200 --> 00:03:54,210
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's fine to talk about dreams, 
but how about reality?</font>

61
00:03:54,770 --> 00:03:57,840
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">How are we going to get out of here?</font>

62
00:03:58,580 --> 00:04:01,760
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">This whole area seems 
to be under a spell,</font>

63
00:04:01,760 --> 00:04:05,470
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">which is why we keep ending 
up at the same place.</font>

64
00:04:05,760 --> 00:04:10,730
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Any kind of magic—even the forbidden 
kind—needs a Casting Seal to work.</font>

65
00:04:11,140 --> 00:04:13,110
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We need to find out where it is and—</font>

66
00:04:13,110 --> 00:04:14,120
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Excuse me.</font>

67
00:04:15,960 --> 00:04:20,510
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I think I saw the Casting Seal... maybe?</font>

68
00:04:21,600 --> 00:04:24,370
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You're right. It's up there.</font>

69
00:04:26,090 --> 00:04:28,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yeah. A Casting Seal.</font>

70
00:04:28,000 --> 00:04:32,190
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Huh? Does that dragon 
look bigger than before?</font>

71
00:04:32,190 --> 00:04:36,170
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Or we're getting smaller 
with the rest of the space.</font>

72
00:04:36,840 --> 00:04:42,010
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Either way, if the dragon is protecting 
the Casting Seal, we'll have to beat it.</font>

73
00:04:42,010 --> 00:04:44,010
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm thinking fire magic—</font>

74
00:04:42,870 --> 00:04:44,010
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Um...</font>

75
00:04:44,950 --> 00:04:49,080
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I don't think your fire spell 
did much to it before.</font>

76
00:04:49,750 --> 00:04:50,470
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Pardon?</font>

77
00:04:50,470 --> 00:04:52,190
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Um, I mean...</font>

78
00:04:52,690 --> 00:04:55,950
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You slowed it down, 
but I don't think you actually hurt it.</font>

79
00:04:56,360 --> 00:05:00,570
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">So... I don't think fire 
is the way to beat it.</font>

80
00:05:02,110 --> 00:05:04,730
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What do you propose, then?</font>

81
00:05:04,730 --> 00:05:05,950
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We don't beat it.</font>

82
00:05:11,960 --> 00:05:15,050
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Are you still mad about what 
I said before or something?!</font>

83
00:05:15,050 --> 00:05:16,210
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">No, no!</font>

84
00:05:16,210 --> 00:05:19,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You and Tetia just gave me an idea...</font>

85
00:05:21,160 --> 00:05:22,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I have a plan.</font>

86
00:05:22,920 --> 00:05:25,350
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I don't know if it'll work, but...</font>

87
00:05:25,350 --> 00:05:26,740
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'd like to try it.</font>

88
00:05:34,510 --> 00:05:35,860
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You mean...</font>

89
00:05:35,860 --> 00:05:37,400
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yes!</font>

90
00:05:37,400 --> 00:05:41,280
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The plan to make Tetia's dream come true!</font>

91
00:05:42,340 --> 00:05:43,610
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What are you talking about?</font>

92
00:05:43,610 --> 00:05:46,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Well, Tetia's cloud made 
us feel warm and safe</font>

93
00:05:46,630 --> 00:05:48,830
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">in this bitter, cold place, right?</font>

94
00:05:48,830 --> 00:05:52,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">So what if we make a 
cloud bed for the dragon,</font>

95
00:05:52,460 --> 00:05:56,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">so it would stay there 
instead of attacking us?</font>

96
00:05:56,380 --> 00:05:58,950
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I doubt it's going to go that—</font>

97
00:05:57,610 --> 00:05:58,950
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">True.</font>

98
00:05:59,420 --> 00:06:02,410
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">All are helpless before 
the power of a warm bed!</font>

99
00:06:02,410 --> 00:06:04,430
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Even dragons, probably!</font>

100
00:06:04,430 --> 00:06:06,010
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yeah, that's right!</font>

101
00:06:06,010 --> 00:06:09,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But... that's...</font>

102
00:06:10,910 --> 00:06:13,980
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Look, give me a minute 
to work through this.</font>

103
00:06:13,980 --> 00:06:17,830
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Humans certainly find warm 
beds irresistible, but...</font>

104
00:06:19,690 --> 00:06:22,530
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Coco? Is something wrong?</font>

105
00:06:22,530 --> 00:06:24,970
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">No, it's nothing!</font>

106
00:06:24,970 --> 00:06:28,090
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I was just wondering 
if the dragon was okay.</font>

107
00:06:29,780 --> 00:06:31,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The dragon?</font>

108
00:06:31,000 --> 00:06:33,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">When we ran away before,</font>

109
00:06:33,670 --> 00:06:37,690
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">it slammed hard into 
a pillar, nose-first.</font>

110
00:06:37,690 --> 00:06:40,930
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">At the time, I was too scared 
to think twice about it,</font>

111
00:06:40,930 --> 00:06:44,720
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">but I'm thinking it was 
probably really painful.</font>

112
00:06:45,800 --> 00:06:49,930
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And that's why, well...</font>

113
00:06:50,350 --> 00:06:53,980
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That's why I thought this 
plan was worth trying!</font>

114
00:06:57,230 --> 00:07:01,730
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Master said that the spells 
that aren't forbidden</font>

115
00:07:01,730 --> 00:07:04,650
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">are the ones that bring happiness to all.</font>

116
00:07:05,220 --> 00:07:09,190
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">So I want to show the dragon 
some kinder magic.</font>

117
00:07:09,990 --> 00:07:14,010
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">If this works, no one has to get hurt.</font>

118
00:07:14,710 --> 00:07:17,950
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Not us, and not the dragon, either!</font>

119
00:07:21,770 --> 00:07:23,010
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Good point!</font>

120
00:07:23,010 --> 00:07:28,840
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And if Agott helps us, 
it'll probably work even better!</font>

121
00:07:28,840 --> 00:07:31,100
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You're acting like you have ideas.</font>

122
00:07:32,860 --> 00:07:36,270
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Well... maybe I do.</font>

123
00:07:36,270 --> 00:07:38,850
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Then let's do this together.</font>

124
00:07:40,340 --> 00:07:44,110
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You're the best at drawing 
seals out of all of us.</font>

125
00:07:44,110 --> 00:07:46,990
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We'll have a much better chance 
if you're on the team.</font>

126
00:07:57,380 --> 00:07:58,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Well...</font>

127
00:08:00,360 --> 00:08:01,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Fine.</font>

128
00:08:01,750 --> 00:08:03,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yay!</font>

129
00:08:03,800 --> 00:08:05,210
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hey, watch it!</font>

130
00:08:08,410 --> 00:08:10,120
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Thanks, Agott!</font>

131
00:08:10,120 --> 00:08:11,450
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Forget about me!</font>

132
00:08:11,450 --> 00:08:13,510
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Let's talk strategy!</font>

133
00:08:13,510 --> 00:08:14,600
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Okay!</font>

134
00:08:17,570 --> 00:08:20,020
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You want to be able to lie on it, right?</font>

135
00:08:20,020 --> 00:08:23,800
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yes, I want it to be like 
a nice, fluffy bed!</font>

136
00:08:23,800 --> 00:08:28,370
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Something as fluffy as a cloud, 
but with proper substance...</font>

137
00:08:28,370 --> 00:08:30,510
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Something we can find here...</font>

138
00:08:30,510 --> 00:08:34,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">...and that could withstand 
a dragon's weight.</font>

139
00:08:35,200 --> 00:08:36,760
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Shredded paper!</font>

140
00:08:36,760 --> 00:08:39,620
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We could tear up all four of our 
Quires and it wouldn't be enough.</font>

141
00:08:39,620 --> 00:08:40,280
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Cloth!</font>

142
00:08:40,280 --> 00:08:41,120
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hair.</font>

143
00:08:41,120 --> 00:08:42,530
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Not nearly enough.</font>

144
00:08:42,530 --> 00:08:44,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And are you willing to give those up?</font>

145
00:08:47,210 --> 00:08:48,410
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Sand...</font>

146
00:08:50,050 --> 00:08:51,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What about sand?</font>

147
00:08:52,970 --> 00:08:54,350
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The Wall Breaker spell!</font>

148
00:08:54,350 --> 00:08:58,600
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We can create a very fine sand 
by busting up the walls and floors.</font>

149
00:08:58,600 --> 00:09:02,230
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Of course! Who doesn't love 
lying on a sandy beach?!</font>

150
00:09:02,230 --> 00:09:04,480
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Smart thinking, Agott! Smartygott!</font>

151
00:09:04,480 --> 00:09:08,270
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The more signs drawn to the seal, 
the finer the sand it will produce.</font>

152
00:09:08,270 --> 00:09:09,820
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">More so if the seals are smaller.</font>

153
00:09:09,820 --> 00:09:12,740
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Leave the tiny seals to Richeh!</font>

154
00:09:13,450 --> 00:09:14,410
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">So fast!</font>

155
00:09:14,410 --> 00:09:16,530
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That's Richeh's specialty!</font>

156
00:09:16,530 --> 00:09:19,970
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Tetia, think of a spell that will 
gather the sand in the central plaza</font>

157
00:09:19,970 --> 00:09:21,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">without packing it too hard.</font>

158
00:09:21,130 --> 00:09:24,600
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'll try to think up an enveloping spell 
that will keep it in place.</font>

159
00:09:24,600 --> 00:09:25,700
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You got it!</font>

160
00:09:25,700 --> 00:09:27,070
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">H-Hey!</font>

161
00:09:29,030 --> 00:09:30,650
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What should I do?</font>

162
00:09:30,650 --> 00:09:32,230
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Just stay out of it.</font>

163
00:09:33,430 --> 00:09:35,260
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I've agreed to your plan,</font>

164
00:09:35,260 --> 00:09:38,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">but you're not at a skill level 
where I can trust you with a spell.</font>

165
00:09:39,390 --> 00:09:41,740
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The best thing you can do 
is stay out of our way.</font>

166
00:09:53,010 --> 00:09:56,910
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>How does she draw such a perfect circle?</i></font>

167
00:10:14,650 --> 00:10:17,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>She draws the circle in 
the air a few times first,</i></font>

168
00:10:17,000 --> 00:10:19,320
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>then starts at the point closest to her.</i></font>

169
00:10:20,290 --> 00:10:23,470
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Do Tetia and Richeh do it the same way?</i></font>

170
00:10:30,270 --> 00:10:33,110
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>How have I been doing it?</i></font>

171
00:10:33,560 --> 00:10:36,590
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>The place to start... the final shape...</i></font>

172
00:10:36,590 --> 00:10:38,800
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I guess I never gave much 
thought to that stuff.</i></font>

173
00:10:41,450 --> 00:10:42,720
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I'm going to try it.</i></font>

174
00:10:43,290 --> 00:10:46,210
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Until I can do it like they can...</i></font>

175
00:10:47,960 --> 00:10:49,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I'm going to try it!</i></font>

176
00:10:50,770 --> 00:10:54,550
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Like this... and then...</font>

177
00:10:55,070 --> 00:10:56,390
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Then this...</font>

178
00:11:09,610 --> 00:11:10,760
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's cold.</font>

179
00:11:11,480 --> 00:11:13,480
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yeah, it's gotten pretty dark, huh?</font>

180
00:11:13,480 --> 00:11:14,780
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Should I start a fire?</font>

181
00:11:14,780 --> 00:11:16,210
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm out of paper.</font>

182
00:11:16,210 --> 00:11:17,720
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">So am I.</font>

183
00:11:18,670 --> 00:11:20,610
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's hopeless.</font>

184
00:11:20,610 --> 00:11:23,220
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">A Sign of Convergence 
would pack it too hard.</font>

185
00:11:23,220 --> 00:11:25,550
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What if you wrap it in a membrane of air?</font>

186
00:11:25,550 --> 00:11:28,020
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Too weak. It'll still fall apart.</font>

187
00:11:28,730 --> 00:11:31,300
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What about reinforcing it 
with fine strips of cloth?</font>

188
00:11:31,300 --> 00:11:33,930
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Just wrapping it up in that 
won't be enough.</font>

189
00:11:33,930 --> 00:11:35,480
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And it's going to get even colder, so—</font>

190
00:11:35,480 --> 00:11:36,510
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Forget it.</font>

191
00:11:37,740 --> 00:11:39,800
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">There's gotta be something...</font>

192
00:11:39,800 --> 00:11:42,820
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}Need an idea... An idea...</font>

193
00:11:41,020 --> 00:11:42,820
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>There must be a way.</i></font>

194
00:11:42,820 --> 00:11:44,610
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>The perfect idea...</i></font>

195
00:11:51,470 --> 00:11:52,330
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I...</font>

196
00:11:53,100 --> 00:11:54,240
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I did it!</font>

197
00:11:56,720 --> 00:11:59,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Um... why are you casting tha—</font>

198
00:11:59,460 --> 00:12:00,990
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's stable.</font>

199
00:12:01,710 --> 00:12:03,140
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">She cast a Pyreball!</font>

200
00:12:03,140 --> 00:12:05,030
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yours used to go out right away, right?</font>

201
00:12:05,030 --> 00:12:07,440
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">When did you learn to make it so good?</font>

202
00:12:07,440 --> 00:12:09,760
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I've been practicing just now.</font>

203
00:12:09,760 --> 00:12:12,090
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I was watching you all do your thing,</font>

204
00:12:12,090 --> 00:12:14,890
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">so I did it over and over until...</font>

205
00:12:17,260 --> 00:12:18,600
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That's amazing!</font>

206
00:12:18,600 --> 00:12:20,640
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Coco, you did it!</font>

207
00:12:21,830 --> 00:12:26,470
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Well, anyone can learn 
with enough repetition...</font>

208
00:12:27,880 --> 00:12:30,600
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Repetition?</font>

209
00:12:31,350 --> 00:12:32,860
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Repetition! That's it!</font>

210
00:12:40,420 --> 00:12:41,740
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Everyone ready?</font>

211
00:12:42,520 --> 00:12:44,140
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Ready anytime.</font>

212
00:12:45,690 --> 00:12:47,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">All right, let's go!</font>

213
00:12:56,300 --> 00:12:57,270
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Coco!</font>

214
00:12:58,310 --> 00:12:59,220
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Thanks!</font>

215
00:12:59,780 --> 00:13:01,800
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's definitely bigger than before.</font>

216
00:13:02,080 --> 00:13:03,970
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We have to finish this quickly.</font>

217
00:13:04,370 --> 00:13:05,810
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Richeh, go on ahead!</font>

218
00:13:05,810 --> 00:13:06,480
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Right.</font>

219
00:13:43,130 --> 00:13:44,170
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Done!</font>

220
00:13:44,170 --> 00:13:45,180
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Coco!</font>

221
00:13:45,180 --> 00:13:45,970
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Right!</font>

222
00:13:49,290 --> 00:13:51,680
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Make the sign to close the rings.</font>

223
00:13:51,680 --> 00:13:52,480
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Right.</font>

224
00:13:53,520 --> 00:13:54,480
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Three...</font>

225
00:13:54,480 --> 00:13:55,730
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Two...</font>

226
00:13:55,990 --> 00:13:56,980
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">One...</font>

227
00:14:04,930 --> 00:14:06,090
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Richeh, next station!</font>

228
00:14:06,090 --> 00:14:06,990
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Right.</font>

229
00:14:31,350 --> 00:14:32,320
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It noticed!</font>

230
00:14:32,320 --> 00:14:33,850
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We need to meet up!</font>

231
00:14:33,850 --> 00:14:35,240
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Did you finish your rings?</font>

232
00:14:35,240 --> 00:14:36,860
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">All activated.</font>

233
00:14:36,860 --> 00:14:38,110
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Great.</font>

234
00:14:38,110 --> 00:14:39,600
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Repetition?</i></font>

235
00:14:39,600 --> 00:14:40,820
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yes.</font>

236
00:14:40,820 --> 00:14:43,350
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">To keep the spell from falling apart,</font>

237
00:14:43,350 --> 00:14:47,740
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">we'll wrap it in repetition magic that 
constantly returns it to its initial form.</font>

238
00:14:48,030 --> 00:14:49,120
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">In other words,</font>

239
00:14:49,120 --> 00:14:54,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">envelop the Wall Breaker/Billow Cluster 
combination in a Repetition Spell</font>

240
00:14:51,990 --> 00:14:53,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}Coco!</font>

241
00:14:54,000 --> 00:14:56,170
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">to create a cloud of sand.</font>

242
00:14:56,170 --> 00:15:00,170
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Given the size of the dragon, 
we'll need five, I think.</font>

243
00:14:56,520 --> 00:14:57,700
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}Current status?</font>

244
00:14:57,700 --> 00:15:00,170
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}It's wary, but almost there...</font>

245
00:15:00,170 --> 00:15:05,180
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">If we can sync the positioning and 
timing right to combine five into one...</font>

246
00:15:05,180 --> 00:15:06,900
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Even if it sinks with the beast's weight,</font>

247
00:15:06,900 --> 00:15:09,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">the sand cloud will keep trying 
to return to its original shape,</font>

248
00:15:09,960 --> 00:15:12,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">and maintain its nice fluffiness.</font>

249
00:15:13,930 --> 00:15:15,310
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I call it...</font>

250
00:15:14,310 --> 00:15:15,310
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I call it...</font>

251
00:15:24,010 --> 00:15:26,680
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The Dragon Disabler Cushion!</font>

252
00:15:27,700 --> 00:15:29,900
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Wrong. It's the Serpent's Bed of Sand.</font>

253
00:15:29,900 --> 00:15:31,320
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That's much cooler!</font>

254
00:15:31,320 --> 00:15:32,320
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Smartygott!</font>

255
00:15:32,320 --> 00:15:33,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Smartygott.</font>

256
00:15:33,380 --> 00:15:34,840
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Enough nonsense.</font>

257
00:15:34,840 --> 00:15:36,830
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Now's our chance to get past it!</font>

258
00:15:40,970 --> 00:15:42,090
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Tetia?</font>

259
00:15:42,540 --> 00:15:43,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What is it?</font>

260
00:15:43,920 --> 00:15:45,970
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, nothing.</font>

261
00:15:46,640 --> 00:15:48,590
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I just couldn't help but look.</font>

262
00:15:49,900 --> 00:15:53,720
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That dragon looks really happy, huh?</font>

263
00:15:54,540 --> 00:16:00,110
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I think this is the first time I've ever 
made someone happy with a spell.</font>

264
00:16:04,020 --> 00:16:07,060
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Who'd have thought 
it'd bring you such joy?</font>

265
00:16:15,250 --> 00:16:16,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Well?</font>

266
00:16:16,290 --> 00:16:19,100
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yeah, I think this is it.</font>

267
00:16:19,100 --> 00:16:20,860
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What kind of spell is it?</font>

268
00:16:20,860 --> 00:16:22,680
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I've never seen it before.</font>

269
00:16:23,750 --> 00:16:26,260
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Master might know, I suppose.</font>

270
00:16:31,310 --> 00:16:32,640
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">They're in here?</font>

271
00:16:35,020 --> 00:16:36,650
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I don't sense anyone.</i></font>

272
00:16:36,650 --> 00:16:38,330
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Did they move on already?</i></font>

273
00:16:38,330 --> 00:16:39,390
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Huh?</font>

274
00:16:39,390 --> 00:16:43,220
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I thought this alley was paved...</font>

275
00:16:43,220 --> 00:16:45,650
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Maybe they removed the 
flagstones at some point.</font>

276
00:16:46,800 --> 00:16:49,690
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Brushbuddies are drawn to 
the smell of Conjuring Ink.</i></font>

277
00:16:51,000 --> 00:16:52,030
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Is this—</font>

278
00:16:55,360 --> 00:16:56,620
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Get back!</font>

279
00:17:06,770 --> 00:17:10,900
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Why didn't you think 
before breaking the seal?!</font>

280
00:17:10,900 --> 00:17:13,530
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's what brought us here, isn't it?!</font>

281
00:17:13,530 --> 00:17:15,180
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Look up, everyone!</font>

282
00:17:15,180 --> 00:17:16,700
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I can see the sky!</font>

283
00:17:17,180 --> 00:17:19,660
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Is that the way out?!</font>

284
00:17:19,660 --> 00:17:20,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Get down!</font>

285
00:17:27,420 --> 00:17:28,570
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Ago—</font>

286
00:17:30,570 --> 00:17:32,280
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>What do I do?</i></font>

287
00:17:32,280 --> 00:17:36,340
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I'm not wearing my Sylph Shoes...</i></font>

288
00:17:48,940 --> 00:17:50,140
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Master?</font>

289
00:17:50,140 --> 00:17:52,430
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">A dragon, is it?</font>

290
00:17:52,430 --> 00:17:53,890
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Master, I—</font>

291
00:17:53,890 --> 00:17:55,760
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's coming. Hang on.</font>

292
00:18:04,850 --> 00:18:07,360
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I need my hands free. Hold on tight!</font>

293
00:18:07,360 --> 00:18:08,350
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yes, sir!</font>

294
00:19:06,370 --> 00:19:08,150
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You're safe now.</font>

295
00:19:08,150 --> 00:19:10,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I think it's unconscious.</font>

296
00:19:11,390 --> 00:19:12,490
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Agott?</font>

297
00:19:13,100 --> 00:19:14,450
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">R-Right...</font>

298
00:19:14,450 --> 00:19:16,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Master!</font>

299
00:19:16,380 --> 00:19:18,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Tetia! Richeh!</font>

300
00:19:17,100 --> 00:19:19,610
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}I was so scared!</font>

301
00:19:18,380 --> 00:19:20,760
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">How did you get here, sir?</font>

302
00:19:20,760 --> 00:19:24,620
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I was searching for you when 
the space opened up around me...</font>

303
00:19:27,620 --> 00:19:28,730
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Where's Coco?</font>

304
00:19:34,520 --> 00:19:36,150
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hello, Coco.</font>

305
00:19:36,980 --> 00:19:42,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I've waited so long for the 
seeds I planted to sprout.</font>

306
00:19:43,910 --> 00:19:47,320
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">How did you like the 
assignment I gave you?</font>

307
00:19:47,750 --> 00:19:50,490
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Did it aid your growth?</font>

308
00:19:50,930 --> 00:19:54,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I know. I'll give you a gift.</font>

309
00:19:55,300 --> 00:20:00,180
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'll teach you things that Qifrey can't.</font>

310
00:20:00,670 --> 00:20:02,430
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And when the day comes...</font>

311
00:20:03,040 --> 00:20:06,780
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yes, what a day that will be!</font>

312
00:20:10,860 --> 00:20:11,870
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Coco!</font>

313
00:20:12,180 --> 00:20:13,430
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Coco!</font>

314
00:20:14,440 --> 00:20:15,770
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Coco!</font>

315
00:20:18,700 --> 00:20:20,660
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Master Qifrey...</font>

316
00:20:21,300 --> 00:20:22,700
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Everyone...</font>

317
00:20:26,290 --> 00:20:27,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Is Agott—</font>

318
00:20:27,130 --> 00:20:28,110
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm right here.</font>

319
00:20:28,640 --> 00:20:30,740
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Thank you for this, Tartah.</font>

320
00:20:31,290 --> 00:20:32,730
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}Sure.</font>

321
00:20:32,730 --> 00:20:35,950
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}I'll see if I can get Grandpa to come by.</font>

322
00:20:34,810 --> 00:20:35,950
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Thank goodness.</font>

323
00:20:36,550 --> 00:20:39,060
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Wait, is this Kalhn?</font>

324
00:20:39,060 --> 00:20:42,350
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yes, we all made it back!</font>

325
00:20:42,350 --> 00:20:44,060
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Thank goodness
I was able to find you.</font>

326
00:20:44,060 --> 00:20:46,520
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You were unconscious on the tower stairs.</font>

327
00:20:46,520 --> 00:20:48,020
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The stairs?</font>

328
00:20:49,750 --> 00:20:52,310
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Wait... did the Brimmed Caps 
do something to you?</font>

329
00:20:52,310 --> 00:20:56,020
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">No! I'm just a little spaced out.</font>

330
00:20:56,020 --> 00:20:57,320
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Um...</font>

331
00:21:03,110 --> 00:21:04,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Coco?</font>

332
00:21:05,520 --> 00:21:06,950
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Are you okay?</font>

333
00:21:08,510 --> 00:21:11,660
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yeah... I'm fine. I'm fi—</font>

334
00:21:24,550 --> 00:21:27,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm sorry.</font>

335
00:21:29,650 --> 00:21:33,220
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I got you all mixed up in this.</font>

336
00:21:34,740 --> 00:21:36,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm really...</font>

337
00:21:37,610 --> 00:21:39,110
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">really sorry.</font>

338
00:21:43,590 --> 00:21:47,740
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}Tetia told me what happened in there.</font>

339
00:21:48,330 --> 00:21:51,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And what you all did there.</font>

340
00:21:53,990 --> 00:21:57,340
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It sounds like you saved them all.</font>

341
00:21:58,810 --> 00:22:03,470
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Ideas are as important to 
spellcasting as penmanship.</font>

342
00:22:03,470 --> 00:22:05,780
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Let's work hard to nurture that talent.</font>

343
00:22:19,480 --> 00:22:20,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Okay!</font>

344
00:22:21,880 --> 00:22:24,990
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}Coco! I'm so glad you're safe!</font>

345
00:22:24,990 --> 00:22:26,950
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}I'm sorry I worried you!</font>

346
00:22:26,950 --> 00:22:28,410
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}I'm sorry, Richeh, and Agott...</font>

347
00:22:28,410 --> 00:22:29,990
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}I wasn't worried.</font>

348
00:22:29,990 --> 00:22:34,400
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}She was totally worried. 
I saw your cloak—</font>

349
00:22:29,990 --> 00:22:32,470
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">They're not just safe, they're thriving!</font>

350
00:22:32,470 --> 00:22:34,400
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yes, thanks to all your help.</font>

351
00:22:34,750 --> 00:22:36,690
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's awfully late.</font>

352
00:22:36,690 --> 00:22:39,050
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Why not get a room at an inn—</font>

353
00:22:39,050 --> 00:22:40,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Mr. Nolnoa.</font>

354
00:22:40,470 --> 00:22:42,650
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I have a serious favor to ask you.</font>

355
00:22:42,650 --> 00:22:43,710
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Eh?</font>

356
00:22:44,380 --> 00:22:47,310
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}There's a Casting Seal 
drawn on the back of this.</font>

357
00:22:47,310 --> 00:22:50,860
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}I need to know what's in the ink.</font>

358
00:22:50,860 --> 00:22:52,830
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}Will you look into it for me?</font>

359
00:22:52,830 --> 00:22:55,550
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}Let's see. What's in the ink?</font>

360
00:22:55,550 --> 00:22:59,770
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}And please don't tell the 
Knights Moralis about this.</font>

361
00:23:00,400 --> 00:23:04,900
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">B-But we have an obligation to 
report Forbidden Magic sightings—</font>

362
00:23:06,740 --> 00:23:08,910
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Do not tell anyone of this.</font>

363
00:23:09,400 --> 00:23:10,720
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Not <i>anyone</i>.</font>

364
00:23:21,430 --> 00:23:24,930
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Honestly. I wonder 
what's happening here...</font>

365
00:23:25,930 --> 00:23:27,560
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}Isn't that Coco's?</font>

366
00:23:27,560 --> 00:23:32,660
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Or perhaps... what's about to happen?</font>

367
00:23:27,560 --> 00:23:31,180
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}Whoops! I forgot.</font>

368
00:23:35,350 --> 00:23:39,940
